{"tid":899102,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"每日都覺得人生好冇意義","createTime":"2018-11-12T07:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T09:12:17.000Z","uid":221759,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"84b33972cc53c588d74deb37f8b5f75444e2b935","tid":899102,"uid":221759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:08:49.000Z","msg":"以下開放自由討論"},{"pid":"abd8f48a921a108227a8e3d1659c54c00f3fa523","tid":899102,"uid":36402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:09:13.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"e7d5b729597b5fa0d1617a34227aa24dc31302ac","tid":899102,"uid":139712,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:18:14.000Z","msg":"我都覺 日日返份唔鐘意既工為左賺個小小錢<br />\n有錢都無時間做自己想做既野<br />\n有時諗 如果唔系為錢都唔會返份工<br />\n系味有錢人既人生先會有意義 唔洗為錢而返工"},{"pid":"95548d90b2f5eb6c8e4c0bbc34d2e85e600edb95","tid":899102,"uid":189157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:19:09.000Z","msg":"創業啦"},{"pid":"e3cac1adc99c6ce75cf2ac2a51d0b537493571a6","tid":899102,"uid":187197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:21:21.000Z","msg":"其實日日都唔知自己做緊乜<br />\n淨係想攤係屋企訓<br />\n唔知搵錢黎做咩，人生冇目標冇方向<br />\n廿幾歲人都仲係咁<br />\n唔通我生存嘅意義就係為左搵我嘅人生意義？"},{"pid":"c06d5f306cde93d218b46948a9cc2d71e47d1aa7","tid":899102,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T07:36:02.000Z","msg":"係 返工放工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  連返工期間都係一個人(無同事)<br />\n放假 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己係屋企<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個人唔outgoing點樣可以擴闊圈子"},{"pid":"4def5ebc0c12c1c022229bbf36f569bac1cba7ee","tid":899102,"uid":49151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T08:14:09.000Z","msg":"冇人生目標 好想出國闖下"},{"pid":"7a6468b81e82b5b35bee8fd713725439b887269d","tid":899102,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-12T09:12:17.000Z","msg":"你又無膽<br />\n而家即刻買張單程機票去外國<br />\n玩夠1年先好番香港囉<br />\n呢樣又驚果樣又驚 然後又係度怨"}]}